tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
context: Wisdom Tooth Extraction,Dental Cleaning,Root Canal Treatment (RCT),PULP Capping,
review:
Ever since I moved to Hyderabad and needed to find a new dentist, I was a little nervous because I had some less than good experiences with another dentists here in Hyderabad and used to travel to my hometown Mumbai for my dental work.
A friend recommended Dr. Anshul at Dentaire who turned out to be fantastic! She answered every question I had and has been very accommodating, reassuring and easy. Dentaire is very well maintained, contemporary clinic with a warm and welcoming team. If you need a dentist, don't hesitate to call Dr. Anshul - She's awesome!
reply_text: Thanks for the wonderful review, Jay! We work hard to meet expectations like yours, and we are happy that we hit the mark for you! Your opinion means the world to us! See you soon! Keep smiling!

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I was extremely paranoid about my visit to the dentist for my root canal. It was amazing to see how well both the doctors calmed me down and patiently worked with me and my paranoia ...

The orthodontist assigned for me was brilliant! He was gentle and very systematic and organized. The medical procedure was explained well and post treatment care as well as the next steps in the procedure was explained in detail by the doctor. 

The doctors in this clinic have good connections with various specialists as well. I must say after this, my faith in dentists has been restored. Thank you very much. 

Regards,
Vaishnavi Shankar

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review:
I approached Dr. Anushal after having pains in my teeth due to cavity and found out that I have to get one of my teeth extracted and the other one treated for cavity.
She Suggested the best treatment
And fixed the problem efficiently and most importantly without any pains. I got my tooth extracted and went back to work just in half an hour. Her approach swept off all the fears I had Before extraction. The clinic was super clean, you can trust them blindfolded. I would always suggest her to anyone who wants to get rid of their dental problems .

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: I had visited the clinic because I had severe pain and swelling in my left jawline extending up to the left ear. Dr. Anshul examined and explained my case in detail. My wisdom teeth were affected and one of them was infected and had to be removed asap. The doctors here are well experienced and know what they are doing. My surgeon, Dr. Kiran extracted my infected lower wisdom tooth and the procedure was so smooth that I asked him to remove the upper wisdom tooth too, which was halfway inside the gum and had cavity. I am very happy with the treatment. Also, the doctors and the staff, especially Dr. Anshul kept a regular check on me until the removal of sutures and complete recovery.
reply_text:
Thanks for the fabulous review, Fabiha! We are delighted to hear about your positive experience and that we could help you overcome your fears. We work hard to meet expectations like yours, and we are happy to hear we hit the mark for you. Your opinion means the world to us! Keep smiling!
-- Team Dentaire

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review: The doctors at Dentaire are very helpful and accommodating. They made the treatment process of multiple root canals and extractions very comfortable for my aunt who cannot walk. They even personally assisted her to and from the car. The doctors made sure she was comfortable at all times with the treatment procedure and every one of them took the time to explain the problem, its cause, treatment and further care to the patient and attender. We had a great experience at dentaire and will recommend it to friends and family.
reply_text:
Dear Kiranmayi, thank you for the amazing review! Kind words like these make us continue our journey towards excellence in dental care. We are glad we could deliver to your expectations. Always in pursuit of excellence!
--Team Dentaire

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: I had  to be treated for tooth removal  so through a friend I came to know about Dr.Anshul. From day 1 of treatment still date I had a smooth journey and everything was explained and done at my convenience and comfort. The process was also done very professional and painless. Post treatment after the tooth removal was taken care perfectly and the doc was just a call away for the entire process. I would definitely recommend the doctor to all as she is extremely good at her work and friendly too.
